though he could have stopped in time to ring the closing 4 pm 
bell at the new york stock exchange gorbachevs motorcade breezed 
past the financial mecca 
his long black limousine decked with a red soviet flag on the 
fender slowed slightly as it turned onto broad street where the 
exchange is located just long enough for the crowd standing 10deep 
