glow with the full eight tapers of the menorahs 
its the religious calendars prelude to christmas which is 
separate but which indirectly hinges on the ancient event marked by 
that effusion of jewish lights 
starting with a customary single candle when the holiday began 
last saturday an additional one was lit on each successive night 
