determination to strictly clamp down on illegal exports of sensitive 
goods to the communist nation 
i take it as something like a hello call to presidentelect 
bush said kazuhisa ogawa a defense analyst and noted author on 
usjapan military relations 
halogenated hydrocarbon is a fluoric compound commonly used in 
fire extinguishers but it can also be used as a coolant for guided 
missiles ogawa said 
