the stock market struggled to a small gain 
wednesday in a muted response to soviet leader mikhail gorbachevs 
speech at the united nations 
the dow jones average of 30 industrials which had risen 5708 
points in the two previous sessions added another 427 to 215363 
advancing issues outnumbered declines by about 5 to 4 in 
nationwide trading of new york stock exchangelisted stocks with 
817 up 632 down and 536 unchanged 
